org.aion.api.type

Class ContractResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aion.api.type.ContractResponse

  • public final class ContractResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    ALl relevant information pertaining to IContract function calls. For non-constant function calls, ContractResponse will contain the transaction msgHash. For constant function calls, ContractResponse will contain an ArrayList of objects.
    Author:
    Jay Tseng
